# Files Mintlify must NOT publish or index.
#
# Mintlify auto-indexes every .md/.mdx under packages/docs/ into the public
# site (and into https://docs.creem.io/llms-full.txt) regardless of docs.json
# navigation. Anything listed here is removed from the published site,
# unreachable by URL, and excluded from search/LLM indexing — but stays in
# the repo so contributors and the Creem API skill plugin can use the files
# locally.
#
# Syntax matches .gitignore.

# Repo-level README that explains how to develop the docs package.
README.md

# Creem API Claude Code skill plugin source. Used by agents that install the
# plugin from this repo; not customer-facing documentation.
skills/
